{"dn20:0.1":"Digha Nikaya 20 ","dn20:0.2":"Mahasamayasutta ","dn20:1.1":"Evam me sutam—","dn20:1.2":"ekam samayam bhagava sakkesu viharati kapilavatthusmim mahavane mahata bhikkhusanghena saddhim pancamattehi bhikkhusatehi sabbeheva arahantehi; ","dn20:1.3":"dasahi ca lokadhatuhi devata yebhuyyena sannipatita honti bhagavantam dassanaya bhikkhusanghanca. ","dn20:2.1":"Atha kho catunnam suddhavasakayikanam devatanam etadahosi: ","dn20:2.2":"“ayam kho bhagava sakkesu viharati kapilavatthusmim mahavane mahata bhikkhusanghena saddhim pancamattehi bhikkhusatehi sabbeheva arahantehi; ","dn20:2.3":"dasahi ca lokadhatuhi devata yebhuyyena sannipatita honti bhagavantam dassanaya bhikkhusanghanca. ","dn20:2.4":"Yannuna mayampi yena bhagava tenupasankameyyama; upasankamitva bhagavato santike paccekam gatham bhaseyyama”ti. ","dn20:3.1":"Atha kho ta devata seyyathapi nama balava puriso saminjitam va baham pasareyya pasaritam va baham saminjeyya; evameva—suddhavasesu devesu antarahita bhagavato purato paturahesum. ","dn20:3.2":"Atha kho ta devata bhagavantam abhivadetva ekamantam atthamsu. ","dn20:3.3":"Ekamantam thita kho eka devata bhagavato santike imam gatham abhasi: ","dn20:3.4":"“Mahasamayo pavanasmim, ","dn20:3.5":"Devakaya samagata; ","dn20:3.6":"Agatamha imam dhammasamayam, ","dn20:3.7":"Dakkhitaye aparajitasanghan”ti. ","dn20:3.8":"Atha kho apara devata bhagavato santike imam gatham abhasi: ","dn20:3.9":"“Tatra bhikkhavo samadahamsu, ","dn20:3.10":"Cittamattano ujukam akamsu; ","dn20:3.11":"Sarathiva nettani gahetva, ","dn20:3.12":"Indriyani rakkhanti pandita”ti. ","dn20:3.13":"Atha kho apara devata bhagavato santike imam gatham abhasi: ","dn20:3.14":"“Chetva khilam chetva paligham, ","dn20:3.15":"Indakhilam uhacca maneja; ","dn20:3.16":"Te caranti suddha vimala, ","dn20:3.17":"Cakkhumata sudanta susunaga”ti. ","dn20:3.18":"Atha kho apara devata bhagavato santike imam gatham abhasi: ","dn20:3.19":"“Ye keci buddham saranam gatase, ","dn20:3.20":"Na te gamissanti apayabhumim; ","dn20:3.21":"Pahaya manusam deham, ","dn20:3.22":"Devakayam paripuressanti”ti. ","dn20:4.0":"1. Devatasannipata ","dn20:4.1":"Atha kho bhagava bhikkhu amantesi: ","dn20:4.2":"“yebhuyyena, bhikkhave, dasasu lokadhatusu devata sannipatita honti, tathagatam dassanaya bhikkhusanghanca. ","dn20:4.3":"Yepi te, bhikkhave, ahesum atitamaddhanam arahanto sammasambuddha, tesampi bhagavantanam etapparamayeva devata sannipatita ahesum seyyathapi mayham etarahi. ","dn20:4.4":"Yepi te, bhikkhave, bhavissanti anagatamaddhanam arahanto sammasambuddha, tesampi bhagavantanam etapparamayeva devata sannipatita bhavissanti seyyathapi mayham etarahi. ","dn20:4.5":"Acikkhissami, bhikkhave, devakayanam namani; ","dn20:4.6":"kittayissami, bhikkhave, devakayanam namani; ","dn20:4.7":"desessami, bhikkhave, devakayanam namani. ","dn20:4.8":"Tam sunatha, sadhukam manasikarotha, bhasissami”ti. ","dn20:4.9":"“Evam, bhante”ti kho te bhikkhu bhagavato paccassosum. ","dn20:4.10":"Bhagava etadavoca: ","dn20:5.1":"“Silokamanukassami, ","dn20:5.2":"yattha bhumma tadassita; ","dn20:5.3":"Ye sita girigabbharam, ","dn20:5.4":"pahitatta samahita. ","dn20:5.5":"Puthusihava sallina, ","dn20:5.6":"lomahamsabhisambhuno; ","dn20:5.7":"Odatamanasa suddha, ","dn20:5.8":"vippasannamanavila. ","dn20:5.9":"Bhiyyo pancasate natva, ","dn20:5.10":"vane kapilavatthave; ","dn20:5.11":"Tato amantayi sattha, ","dn20:5.12":"savake sasane rate. ","dn20:5.13":"‘Devakaya abhikkanta, ","dn20:5.14":"te vijanatha bhikkhavo’; ","dn20:5.15":"Te ca atappamakarum, ","dn20:5.16":"sutva buddhassa sasanam. ","dn20:6.1":"Tesam paturahu nanam, ","dn20:6.2":"amanussanadassanam; ","dn20:6.3":"Appeke satamaddakkhum, ","dn20:6.4":"sahassam atha sattarim. ","dn20:6.5":"Satam eke sahassanam, ","dn20:6.6":"amanussanamaddasum; ","dn20:6.7":"Appekenantamaddakkhum, ","dn20:6.8":"disa sabba phuta ahum. ","dn20:6.9":"Tanca sabbam abhinnaya, ","dn20:6.10":"vavatthitvana cakkhuma; ","dn20:6.11":"Tato amantayi sattha, ","dn20:6.12":"savake sasane rate. ","dn20:6.13":"‘Devakaya abhikkanta, ","dn20:6.14":"te vijanatha bhikkhavo; ","dn20:6.15":"Ye voham kittayissami, ","dn20:6.16":"girahi anupubbaso’. ","dn20:7.1":"Sattasahassa te yakkha, ","dn20:7.2":"bhumma kapilavatthava; ","dn20:7.3":"Iddhimanto jutimanto, ","dn20:7.4":"vannavanto yasassino; ","dn20:7.5":"Modamana abhikkamum, ","dn20:7.6":"bhikkhunam samitim vanam. ","dn20:7.7":"Chasahassa hemavata, ","dn20:7.8":"yakkha nanattavannino; ","dn20:7.9":"Iddhimanto jutimanto, ","dn20:7.10":"vannavanto yasassino; ","dn20:7.11":"Modamana abhikkamum, ","dn20:7.12":"bhikkhunam samitim vanam. ","dn20:7.13":"Satagira tisahassa, ","dn20:7.14":"yakkha nanattavannino; ","dn20:7.15":"Iddhimanto jutimanto, ","dn20:7.16":"vannavanto yasassino; ","dn20:7.17":"Modamana abhikkamum, ","dn20:7.18":"bhikkhunam samitim vanam. ","dn20:7.19":"Iccete solasasahassa, ","dn20:7.20":"yakkha nanattavannino; ","dn20:7.21":"Iddhimanto jutimanto, ","dn20:7.22":"vannavanto yasassino; ","dn20:7.23":"Modamana abhikkamum, ","dn20:7.24":"bhikkhunam samitim vanam. ","dn20:8.1":"Vessamitta pancasata, ","dn20:8.2":"yakkha nanattavannino; ","dn20:8.3":"Iddhimanto jutimanto, ","dn20:8.4":"vannavanto yasassino; ","dn20:8.5":"Modamana abhikkamum, ","dn20:8.6":"bhikkhunam samitim vanam. ","dn20:8.7":"Kumbhiro rajagahiko, ","dn20:8.8":"vepullassa nivesanam; ","dn20:8.9":"Bhiyyo nam satasahassam, ","dn20:8.10":"yakkhanam payirupasati; ","dn20:8.11":"Kumbhiro rajagahiko, ","dn20:8.12":"sopaga samitim vanam. ","dn20:9.1":"Purimanca disam raja, ","dn20:9.2":"dhatarattho pasasati; ","dn20:9.3":"Gandhabbanam adhipati, ","dn20:9.4":"maharaja yasassiso. ","dn20:9.5":"Puttapi tassa bahavo, ","dn20:9.6":"indanama mahabbala; ","dn20:9.7":"Iddhimanto jutimanto, ","dn20:9.8":"vannavanto yasassino; ","dn20:9.9":"Modamana abhikkamum, ","dn20:9.10":"bhikkhunam samitim vanam. ","dn20:9.11":"Dakkhinanca disam raja, ","dn20:9.12":"virulho tam pasasati; ","dn20:9.13":"Kumbhandanam adhipati, ","dn20:9.14":"maharaja yasassiso. ","dn20:9.15":"Puttapi tassa bahavo, ","dn20:9.16":"indanama mahabbala; ","dn20:9.17":"Iddhimanto jutimanto, ","dn20:9.18":"vannavanto yasassino; ","dn20:9.19":"Modamana abhikkamum, ","dn20:9.20":"bhikkhunam samitim vanam. ","dn20:9.21":"Pacchimanca disam raja, ","dn20:9.22":"virupakkho pasasati; ","dn20:9.23":"Nagananca adhipati, ","dn20:9.24":"maharaja yasassiso. ","dn20:9.25":"Puttapi tassa bahavo, ","dn20:9.26":"indanama mahabbala; ","dn20:9.27":"Iddhimanto jutimanto, ","dn20:9.28":"vannavanto yasassino; ","dn20:9.29":"Modamana abhikkamum, ","dn20:9.30":"bhikkhunam samitim vanam. ","dn20:9.31":"Uttaranca disam raja, ","dn20:9.32":"kuvero tam pasasati; ","dn20:9.33":"Yakkhananca adhipati, ","dn20:9.34":"maharaja yasassiso. ","dn20:9.35":"Puttapi tassa bahavo, ","dn20:9.36":"indanama mahabbala; ","dn20:9.37":"Iddhimanto jutimanto, ","dn20:9.38":"vannavanto yasassino; ","dn20:9.39":"Modamana abhikkamum, ","dn20:9.40":"bhikkhunam samitim vanam. ","dn20:9.41":"Purimam disam dhatarattho, ","dn20:9.42":"dakkhinena virulhako; ","dn20:9.43":"Pacchimena virupakkho, ","dn20:9.44":"kuvero uttaram disam. ","dn20:9.45":"Cattaro te maharaja, ","dn20:9.46":"samanta caturo disa; ","dn20:9.47":"Daddallamana atthamsu, ","dn20:9.48":"vane kapilavatthave. ","dn20:10.1":"Tesam mayavino dasa, ","dn20:10.2":"agum vancanika satha; ","dn20:10.3":"Maya kutendu vitendu, ","dn20:10.4":"vitucca vituto saha. ","dn20:10.5":"Candano kamasettho ca, ","dn20:10.6":"kinnighandu nighandu ca; ","dn20:10.7":"Panado opamanno ca, ","dn20:10.8":"devasuto ca matali. ","dn20:10.9":"Cittaseno ca gandhabbo, ","dn20:10.10":"naloraja janesabho; ","dn20:10.11":"Aga pancasikho ceva, ","dn20:10.12":"timbaru suriyavacchasa. ","dn20:10.13":"Ete canne ca rajano, ","dn20:10.14":"gandhabba saha rajubhi; ","dn20:10.15":"Modamana abhikkamum, ","dn20:10.16":"bhikkhunam samitim vanam. ","dn20:11.1":"Athagum nagasa naga, ","dn20:11.2":"vesala sahatacchaka; ","dn20:11.3":"Kambalassatara agum, ","dn20:11.4":"payaga saha natibhi. ","dn20:11.5":"Yamuna dhatarattha ca, ","dn20:11.6":"agu naga yasassino; ","dn20:11.7":"Eravano mahanago, ","dn20:11.8":"sopaga samitim vanam. ","dn20:11.9":"Ye nagaraje sahasa haranti, ","dn20:11.10":"Dibba dija pakkhi visuddhacakkhu; ","dn20:11.11":"Vehayasa te vanamajjhapatta, ","dn20:11.12":"Citra supanna iti tesa namam. ","dn20:11.13":"Abhayam tada nagarajanamasi, ","dn20:11.14":"Supannato khemamakasi buddho; ","dn20:11.15":"Sanhahi vacahi upavhayanta, ","dn20:11.16":"Naga supanna saranamakamsu buddham. ","dn20:12.1":"Jita vajirahatthena, ","dn20:12.2":"samuddam asurasita; ","dn20:12.3":"Bhataro vasavassete, ","dn20:12.4":"iddhimanto yasassino. ","dn20:12.5":"Kalakanca mahabhisma, ","dn20:12.6":"asura danaveghasa; ","dn20:12.7":"Vepacitti sucitti ca, ","dn20:12.8":"paharado namuci saha. ","dn20:12.9":"Satanca baliputtanam, ","dn20:12.10":"sabbe verocanamaka; ","dn20:12.11":"Sannayhitva balisenam, ","dn20:12.12":"rahubhaddamupagamum; ","dn20:12.13":"‘Samayo dani bhaddante, ","dn20:12.14":"bhikkhunam samitim vanam’. ","dn20:13.1":"Apo ca deva pathavi, ","dn20:13.2":"tejo vayo tadagamum; ","dn20:13.3":"Varuna varana deva, ","dn20:13.4":"somo ca yasasa saha. ","dn20:13.5":"Metta karuna kayika, ","dn20:13.6":"agum deva yasassino; ","dn20:13.7":"Dasete dasadha kaya, ","dn20:13.8":"sabbe nanattavannino. ","dn20:13.9":"Iddhimanto jutimanto, ","dn20:13.10":"vannavanto yasassino; ","dn20:13.11":"Modamana abhikkamum, ","dn20:13.12":"bhikkhunam samitim vanam. ","dn20:14.1":"Vendudeva sahali ca, ","dn20:14.2":"asama ca duve yama; ","dn20:14.3":"Candassupanisa deva, ","dn20:14.4":"candamagum purakkhatva. ","dn20:14.5":"Suriyassupanisa deva, ","dn20:14.6":"suriyamagum purakkhatva; ","dn20:14.7":"Nakkhattani purakkhatva, ","dn20:14.8":"agum mandavalahaka. ","dn20:14.9":"Vasunam vasavo settho, ","dn20:14.10":"sakkopaga purindado; ","dn20:14.11":"Dasete dasadha kaya, ","dn20:14.12":"sabbe nanattavannino. ","dn20:14.13":"Iddhimanto jutimanto, ","dn20:14.14":"vannavanto yasassino; ","dn20:14.15":"Modamana abhikkamum, ","dn20:14.16":"bhikkhunam samitim vanam. ","dn20:15.1":"Athagum sahabhu deva, ","dn20:15.2":"jalamaggi sikhariva; ","dn20:15.3":"Aritthaka ca roja ca, ","dn20:15.4":"umapupphanibhasino. ","dn20:15.5":"Varuna sahadhamma ca, ","dn20:15.6":"accuta ca anejaka; ","dn20:15.7":"Suleyyarucira agum, ","dn20:15.8":"agum vasavanesino; ","dn20:15.9":"Dasete dasadha kaya, ","dn20:15.10":"sabbe nanattavannino. ","dn20:15.11":"Iddhimanto jutimanto, ","dn20:15.12":"vannavanto yasassino; ","dn20:15.13":"Modamana abhikkamum, ","dn20:15.14":"bhikkhunam samitim vanam. ","dn20:16.1":"Samana mahasamana, ","dn20:16.2":"manusa manusuttama; ","dn20:16.3":"Khiddapadosika agum, ","dn20:16.4":"agum manopadosika. ","dn20:16.5":"Athagum harayo deva, ","dn20:16.6":"ye ca lohitavasino; ","dn20:16.7":"Paraga mahaparaga, ","dn20:16.8":"agum deva yasassino; ","dn20:16.9":"Dasete dasadha kaya, ","dn20:16.10":"sabbe nanattavannino. ","dn20:16.11":"Iddhimanto jutimanto, ","dn20:16.12":"vannavanto yasassino; ","dn20:16.13":"Modamana abhikkamum, ","dn20:16.14":"bhikkhunam samitim vanam. ","dn20:17.1":"Sukka karambha aruna, ","dn20:17.2":"agum veghanasa saha; ","dn20:17.3":"Odatagayha pamokkha, ","dn20:17.4":"agum deva vicakkhana. ","dn20:17.5":"Sadamatta haragaja, ","dn20:17.6":"missaka ca yasassino; ","dn20:17.7":"Thanayam aga pajjunno, ","dn20:17.8":"yo disa abhivassati. ","dn20:17.9":"Dasete dasadha kaya, ","dn20:17.10":"sabbe nanattavannino; ","dn20:17.11":"Iddhimanto jutimanto, ","dn20:17.12":"vannavanto yasassino; ","dn20:17.13":"Modamana abhikkamum, ","dn20:17.14":"bhikkhunam samitim vanam. ","dn20:18.1":"Khemiya tusita yama, ","dn20:18.2":"katthaka ca yasassino; ","dn20:18.3":"Lambitaka lamasettha, ","dn20:18.4":"jotinama ca asava; ","dn20:18.5":"Nimmanaratino agum, ","dn20:18.6":"athagum paranimmita. ","dn20:18.7":"Dasete dasadha kaya, ","dn20:18.8":"sabbe nanattavannino; ","dn20:18.9":"Iddhimanto jutimanto, ","dn20:18.10":"vannavanto yasassino; ","dn20:18.11":"Modamana abhikkamum, ","dn20:18.12":"bhikkhunam samitim vanam. ","dn20:19.1":"Satthete devanikaya, ","dn20:19.2":"sabbe nanattavannino; ","dn20:19.3":"Namanvayena agacchum, ","dn20:19.4":"ye canne sadisa saha. ","dn20:19.5":"‘Pavutthajatimakhilam, ","dn20:19.6":"oghatinnamanasavam; ","dn20:19.7":"Dakkhemoghataram nagam, ","dn20:19.8":"candamva asitatigam’. ","dn20:20.1":"Subrahma paramatto ca, ","dn20:20.2":"putta iddhimato saha; ","dn20:20.3":"Sanankumaro tisso ca, ","dn20:20.4":"sopaga samitim vanam. ","dn20:20.5":"Sahassam brahmalokanam, ","dn20:20.6":"mahabrahmabhititthati; ","dn20:20.7":"Upapanno jutimanto, ","dn20:20.8":"bhismakayo yasassiso. ","dn20:20.9":"Dasettha issara agum, ","dn20:20.10":"paccekavasavattino; ","dn20:20.11":"Tesanca majjhato aga, ","dn20:20.12":"harito parivarito. ","dn20:21.1":"Te ca sabbe abhikkante, ","dn20:21.2":"sainde deve sabrahmake; ","dn20:21.3":"Marasena abhikkami, ","dn20:21.4":"passa kanhassa mandiyam. ","dn20:21.5":"‘Etha ganhatha bandhatha, ","dn20:21.6":"ragena baddhamatthu vo; ","dn20:21.7":"Samanta parivaretha, ","dn20:21.8":"ma vo muncittha koci nam’. ","dn20:21.9":"Iti tattha mahaseno, ","dn20:21.10":"kanho senam apesayi; ","dn20:21.11":"Panina talamahacca, ","dn20:21.12":"saram katvana bheravam. ","dn20:21.13":"Yatha pavussako megho, ","dn20:21.14":"thanayanto savijjuko; ","dn20:21.15":"Tada so paccudavatti, ","dn20:21.16":"sankuddho asayamvase. ","dn20:22.1":"Tanca sabbam abhinnaya, ","dn20:22.2":"vavatthitvana cakkhuma; ","dn20:22.3":"Tato amantayi sattha, ","dn20:22.4":"savake sasane rate. ","dn20:22.5":"‘Marasena abhikkanta, ","dn20:22.6":"te vijanatha bhikkhavo’; ","dn20:22.7":"Te ca atappamakarum, ","dn20:22.8":"sutva buddhassa sasanam; ","dn20:22.9":"Vitaragehi pakkamum, ","dn20:22.10":"nesam lomapi injayum. ","dn20:22.11":"‘Sabbe vijitasangama, ","dn20:22.12":"bhayatita yasassino; ","dn20:22.13":"Modanti saha bhutehi, ","dn20:22.14":"savaka te janesuta’”ti. ","dn20:22.15":"Mahasamayasuttam nitthitam sattamam. "}